## Welcome to Tacticus

One of the biggest challenges for new players is deciding where to spend limited resources. Tacticus offers many game modes, events, and characters, but not all investments provide the same long-term value.

The goal of this guide is to help new players prioritize their efforts and avoid common progression traps.

## Campaigns Come First

For most new accounts, Campaign progression should be the highest priority.

Campaigns unlock:

* Additional characters
* New game modes
* Better farming locations
* Upgrade materials
* Elite Campaigns

When deciding where to spend resources, ask a simple question:

**Will this help me progress further in a Campaign?**

If the answer is yes, it is usually a good investment.

## Focus Your Resources

A common beginner mistake is trying to upgrade every character.

Instead:

* Prioritize Campaign-required characters.
* Build a small core roster.
* Expand only when new content requires it.

A few strong characters will carry an account much farther than a large collection of underdeveloped ones.

## Understanding Game Modes

Most game modes serve one of two purposes:

* Helping you unlock or strengthen characters.
* Providing resources that support Campaign progression.

While every mode has value, Campaigns are often the foundation that enables success elsewhere in the game.

## Progress Is More Important Than Perfection

There is no single "correct" way to play Tacticus.

The most successful accounts are built through consistent daily progress, smart resource management, and long-term planning.

Don't worry about maximizing every event or competing with veteran players. Focus on unlocking campaigns, strengthening key characters, and steadily expanding your roster over time.

## How to Use This Guide

This infographic recommends where new players should invest resources and which game modes deserve the most attention at different stages of account progression.

Use it as a roadmap, not a rulebook. Every account is different, but Campaign progression remains one of the most reliable paths to long-term success.

